  <FAQs
    title="Still have some doubts?"
    id="faq"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'What does this app do?',
        description:
          'VarsCalculator App allows you to save, manage, and calculate custom expressions using variables (X, Y, Z), making repetitive and complex calculations effortless.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How can this app solve my problem?',
        description:
          'It simplifies calculations by letting you save frequently used formulas and quickly update results by changing variable values, saving you time and reducing errors.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Is it available for my device?',
        description: `VarsCalculator App is designed for compatibility with most smartphones and tablets, ensuring you can calculate on the go, anytime.`,
      },
      {
        title: 'What makes this app different from others?',
        description:
          'VarsCalculator App stands apart with its innovative variable-based calculator, custom expressions, and an integrated history feature, all wrapped in an intuitive and efficient design.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Are there any costs involved?',
        description:
